frames.caption: A young child rides a majestic white Pegasus through a breathtaking mountain landscape. The sky is filled with fluffy clouds, and a bird soars nearby, adding to the sense of freedom and adventure.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical journey through a serene and expansive mountain range. The child and Pegasus are mid-flight, surrounded by towering peaks and a vast, open sky.

frames.caption: A young boy rides a majestic white pegasus through a breathtaking mountainous landscape. The sky is filled with fluffy clouds and birds soaring high, creating a sense of freedom and adventure.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a boy is riding a flying horse, known as a pegasus, amidst towering mountains and a vast sky. The atmosphere is serene and adventurous, evoking a sense of wonder and exploration.
